Alnatura Logo
The Alnatura Produktions- und Handels GmbH is a chain of organic food supermarkets and producer of organic food headquartered in Darmstadt, Hesse in Germany. Alnatura currently operates 107 supermarkets in Germany, each with 500 to 800 square meters of retail space, mainly in Baden-Wuerttemberg, Hesse and Rhineland-Palatinate. The company’s first supermarket opened in Mannheim, Baden-Wuerttemberg on October 1, 1987. Products of Alnatura are also marketed in the stores of dm-drogerie markt and Tegut.

item.title: Alnatura
